  <entry>
    <title>Hello World</title>
    <link href="https://blog.ling71.cn/posts/1243066710.html"/>
    <id>https://blog.ling71.cn/posts/1243066710.html</id>
    <published>2022-02-05T04:18:31.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-02-11T15:10:53.561Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Welcome to <a href="https://hexo.io/">Hexo</a>! </p><h2 id="开始"><a href="#开始" class="headerlink" title="开始"></a>开始</h2><h3 id="创建新文章"><a href="#创建新文章" class="headerlink" title="创建新文章"></a>创建新文章</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo new <span class="string">&quot;My New Post&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>更多信息: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/writing.html">Writing</a></p><h3 id="Run-server"><a href="#Run-server" class="headerlink" title="Run server"></a>Run server</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo server</span><br><span class="line">或者</span><br><span class="line">$ hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>更多信息: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/server.html">Server</a></p><h3 id="生成静态文件"><a href="#生成静态文件" class="headerlink" title="生成静态文件"></a>生成静态文件</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo generate</span><br><span class="line">或者</span><br><span class="line">$ hexo g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>更多信息: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/generating.html">Generating</a></p><h3 id="部署到远程站点"><a href="#部署到远程站点" class="headerlink" title="部署到远程站点"></a>部署到远程站点</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo deploy</span><br><span class="line">或者</span><br><span class="line">$ hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>更多信息: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/one-command-deployment.html">Deployment</a></p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
